(Tertiary Reform) Amendment Act 2002</amending-leg> (2002 No 50).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM84641"><amended-provision>Section 4</amended-provision><emphasis style="bold">Commission</emphasis>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 January
2003</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM166273">section 59</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education
