            <history-note id="DLM2052664"><amended-provision>Section 13(1)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 January 2003</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM166273">section 59</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Education
